  UndoMgr --> BufferPool
  UndoMgr --> Fsp
  UndoMgr --> Redo

  LockMgr --> WaitGraph
  WaitGraph --> Deadlock
  LockMgr --> Trx

  PurgeCoord --> PurgeView
